\begin_inset Formula $\left(t,\varepsilon\right)$
\end_inset

 
\series bold
Existential Unforgeability under Chosen Plaintext Attack 
\series default
if for every 
\begin_inset Formula $t$
\end_inset

-bounded adversary 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{A}$
\end_inset

 which is allowed to ask for 
\begin_inset Formula $t$
\end_inset

 legal pairs,
 
\begin_inset Formula $\Pr\left[\mathcal{A}\text{ wins}\right]\leq\varepsilon$
\end_inset

.
